  <h2 class="business">Business</h2>
<p>Time to bust out the pumps and oxfords with your best pant suit! Business attire can range from casual to formal business wear, but all have the same core pieces. Suit pants, nice skirts, blouses, shirts, and closed toe shoes (excluding sneakers) are all acceptable. Items like jeans, sandals, short clothing or tees are not allowed for business-casual venues.</p><br>
<p>"The idea is to wear something business appropriate that also feels dressed-up."</p>
