  <h2 class="formal">Formal</h2>
  <p>Most people aren't required to dress formally during the week, but once in awhile you may be required to glam up. Formal wear can range in price and fanciness depending on the event. As a rule, women are expected to wear gowns or dresses with pumps or evening shoes. Men are required to wear suits and dress shoes. Cities like London and New York have the largest amount of venues requiring formal wear.</p><br>
  <p>"You aren’t expected to look as if you’re en route the Oscars, but you should still make an effort with formal attire.""</p>
